1.title: Korean Neighborhood: Insadong (Korea Virtual Tour)
1.plot: Hello, this is Double Trouble en Corea. We will be showing you around Insadong but with a slight twist. Check out the Virtual Tour of Korea. Come explore the Korean culture and beautiful landmarks together. See you next time~!.

2.title: Do Not Enter! Double Trouble Vlog
2.plot: Hello, this is Double Trouble en Corea. Today, we visited Gwanghwamun and Itaewon. We also made a delicious dinner, so check out what we made. See you next time~!.

3.title: Vlog Diaries in Korea
3.plot: We will try to vlog every day, to see how it goes, so send lots of fun. ^^ If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe and share!.

4.title: Night Picnic in Korea
4.plot: Today, we went on a picnic to the Han River with Angelina to celebrate the independence of Mexico and Chile. If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe and share!.

5.title: Korean Food Challenge: Jjamppong
5.plot: Hello, everyone. Today, we invited our friends from "My Korean Husband" and challenged them to eat a giant bowl of jjamppong (spicy seafood noodle soup). Can you guess who won?.

6.title: Low-budget Living in Korea
6.plot: Many times, you guys have asked us how we can travel to or live in Korea. Here, we provide a few tricks for saving money in Korea. If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe!.

7.title: Eating for a Week in Korea with 1EUR Experiment
7.plot: "The Vice Magazine" subscribers and some Spaniards have challenged us to eat for a week with only 1 Euro a day, and we found it interesting. So, in this vlog today, we decided to try it. If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe!.

8.title: Makeup Tutorial with Korean Products
8.plot: As you can see, we do not know much about makeup, but hey, we made the attempt for you. Hopefully they like it and you know, if they want to buy some makeup, here we leave the list of products that we asked StyleKorean.

9.title: We Don't Know Our Makeup: Catrina Makeup Fail!
9.plot: Hello, we're Double Trouble en Corea. Today, we decided to do Catrina makeup. But this is just what happend - If you like the video, do not forget to subscribe and share!.

10.title: Korean Food: Dalk Galbi
10.plot: Today, we went to eat a very popular dish in Korea called Dalk Galbi, which is basically stir-fried chicken and several other ingredients. It's delicious. If you do not know about this dish, I check it out. If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe and share. ^^ Stay tuned!.

11.title: Things We Bought at the Supermarket!
11.plot: Today, we went to the supermarket and these are the things we bought. If you liked the video, do not forget to subscribe. Stay tuned!.

imdb.title: Double Trouble En Corea
plot: Hello. We're Diana + Gisela, two Mexican sisters living in Seoul and sharing our experiences, stories + much more as foreigners in Korea. We love creating new and original content for you to enjoy and have fun with!.
